{"tid":258931,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友寧願同fd出去都唔同我出","createTime":"2017-05-26T13:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T14:36:50.000Z","uid":15352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbbfa5a245f6035462ce6656ee82cbc6bc23a07c","tid":258931,"uid":15352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:50:07.000Z","msg":"前幾日問我男朋友不如今日約出黎見好冇<br />\n佢話唔想 不如過多日先見<br />\n點知今日佢又同fd篤波又食晚飯<br />\n我約佢又唔出 fd約佢就出<br />\n原來我喺佢心目中嘅地位已經低過佢啲fd <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n熱戀期就已經咁 遲下點算喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d10590f55f78b8097225c9f5335fbb0663e8d50","tid":258931,"uid":22175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">帽事嘅</span>"},{"pid":"ea69bc7dc0fa59be6e584cfec2d045d467e9f3fb","tid":258931,"uid":20217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:57:04.000Z","msg":"我ex最後個陣都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後講講下忍唔住叫佢重視下我得唔得<br />\n再然後，就沒有然後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d1a5d73cf040842c74f2378559fb9d7b2273a8","tid":258931,"uid":15352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:57:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\">帽事嘅</span></blockquote><br />\n我信佢唔會咁對我架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5b0c7809f80928d7ccd930ca46a235778fa9d5","tid":258931,"uid":15352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我ex最後個陣都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後講講下忍唔住叫佢重視下我得唔得<br />\n再然後，就沒有然後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會唔會最尾都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25e88b50a2e1405fa727cf79962f62b821e11f0","